      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 15:32:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SpaceX 发射两辆月球探测器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/spacex-launces-two-lunar-rovers-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着私营部门的登月竞赛愈演愈烈，SpaceX 于周三发射了一枚猎鹰 9 号火箭，火箭上载有两颗商业卫星和月球车。客户是美国和日本公司。他们共乘一趟以节省成本。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/spacex-launces-two-lunar-rovers-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 14:55:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
